Author: Exile13#4458
Content:
when the pool has little users, it doesnt find blocks as fast, but when they are found the rewards are greater because they are only split between those people
when you have more people you find more blocks but the rewards are less because they are split between many people
i would go with the bigger pool if you want more regular payouts, but with the infancy many things can potentially change
